    • getPseudoDestructor

      ICPPFunction getPseudoDestructor()
      Get the built-in type's pseudo-destructor. The pseudo-destructor is the function named by e.g. an id-expression of the form "T().~T" when instantiated with T mapped to a built-in type.
      Since:
      6.5
